Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.95,0:00:03.64,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,N-No more...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.45,0:00:07.23,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I'm so embarrassed, I could die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:09.92,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,There's no need to be embarrassed. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.39,0:00:29.98,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,No, Kanie! We can't go any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:34.26,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,S-Stop! Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:40.02,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,How can I take you seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:43.02,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,when you're clearly enjoying it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:44.58,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:52.40,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.43,0:00:58.82,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.19,0:01:01.10,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,No, oww—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:03.38,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Y-You can't, no more or I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.99,0:01:05.42,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,No, no more!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.42,0:01:07.58,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Sounds like you're getting close to finishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.61,0:01:13.38,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Stop, no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:26.77,Signs,,0,0,0,,The 25 Year Old High School Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:26.77,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Episode 7: Private Study Session
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.31,0:01:31.00,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You're actually going straight to class, Natori?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:34.16,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,If I don't, there's no point in my being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:36.41,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Besides, we have exams soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.41,0:01:40.03,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, you did terribly on that quiz the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:43.31,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,W-What did you expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.31,0:01:45.79,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,It's not like I've had to study since graduating.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.15,0:01:48.46,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Alright, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:51.79,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Leave your schedule open tomorrow after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:55.46,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I'll teach you how to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.11,0:01:56.84,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.03,0:02:05.00,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How did this happen? How did I end up in Kanie's apartment?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:07.87,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Here. You're good with coffee, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.87,0:02:08.46,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:10.23,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Oh,  t-thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.75,0:02:11.28,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.09,0:02:13.11,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:14.84,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,N-Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.37,0:02:19.03,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Oh, did you think I was going to do something to you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:23.27,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Could it be that a part of you was {\i1}hoping{\i0} I would?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.27,0:02:24.45,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Y-You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.01,0:02:27.21,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Your face is bright red.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:29.42,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I said it's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:33.96,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, Kanie...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.93,0:02:37.08,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Don't worry,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,0:02:38.25,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I won't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:38.76,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:40.71,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.71,0:02:43.22,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Now get to work already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.65,0:02:45.04,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.23,0:02:49.98,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,To begin with, I want to know your abilities, so start with this bit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.55,0:02:53.71,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is so difficult...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:56.61,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could I really work out stuff like this back then?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:02:59.82,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Well, you won't master the subject overnight,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:02.18,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,but I can at least teach you the fundamentals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:04.62,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Be sure to ask if you don't understand anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.05,0:03:05.70,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.67,0:03:09.94,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Say, Kanie, do you wear those because you have poor eyesight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.43,0:03:12.88,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You wear them during class, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:14.96,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,It's not all that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:17.13,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,But it's easier with them, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.83,0:03:20.47,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Do you like me better this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:24.97,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,That's... That's not why I asked...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:30.97,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,It's backwards from when we were in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:31.69,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:35.92,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I'm going to wash up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:38.11,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You keep working.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.77,0:03:43.11,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did something happen when we were students?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.97,0:03:57.59,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,This may be a more serious problem than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:04:00.51,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I really tried my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:01.95,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Well, that's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:03.89,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,We've got plenty of time, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:08.98,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,B-But, if it gets too late, I won't get home on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:11.10,Signs,,0,0,0,,****day **/**
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.51,0:04:11.10,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Just stay over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:13.06,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Wha...What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:17.00,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I said I'd help you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:17.56,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:19.08,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,So listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:21.18,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:28.44,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't tell if Kanie is being nice, or just pushy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:41.07,Songs,,0,0,0,,Who could have predicted this reunion?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.07,0:04:48.87,Songs,,0,0,0,,I reel in this thread of memory, and use it to spin my tale
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:53.75,Songs,,0,0,0,,Why are you all pushy one minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:59.51,Songs,,0,0,0,,and then gentle the next?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:05.01,Songs,,0,0,0,,As long as the two of us share this secret
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:10.57,Songs,,0,0,0,,it will be the light that guides you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:15.35,Songs,,0,0,0,,to somewhere in the yet-unknowable future
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:19.79,Songs,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, it's okay to optimistic
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:23.83,Songs,,0,0,0,,I want to know everything about you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:29.27,Songs,,0,0,0,,hidden deep within those eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:34.53,Songs,,0,0,0,,I can't control these feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:41.69,Songs,,0,0,0,,Piece by piece, my heart is being snatched away
